{"tid":2227810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賀一誠：提升金融業在澳門本地生產總值中比例","createTime":"2020-10-03T05:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T13:26:32.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4bdcba30b0147664cb1bb10e290e0c6a25fab2","tid":2227810,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"澳門行政長官賀一誠表示，希望提升金融業在本地生產總值中的比例。<br />\n<br />\n澳門新聞局深夜發出行政長官賀一誠在政府總部，會見中國企業協會會長傅建國一行的新聞稿。指雙方就疫情防控和澳門經濟適度多元等議題交換意見。賀一誠表示，除繼續以旅遊博彩為澳門主要產業，今後幾年亦會啟動多項公共工程，基礎建設帶動澳門經濟發展。<br />\n<br />\n當提到希望提升金融業佔比時，賀一誠建議駐澳門中資企業能在發展債券市場和特色金融產品等方面，給予更有力支持。他強調，建設粵澳（橫琴）深度合作區是促進澳門適度多元重要方向之一，期望各駐澳中資企業能多加協助，合作發展橫琴島。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548978-20200911.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548978-20200911.htm&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=73e8dc58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548978-20200911.htm&h=6d569388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548978-20200911.htm</a>"},{"pid":"88b431916f8775f8b13d416d1114b63e22b57cac","tid":2227810,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0016e91192673655db5ddd3aa0834fe991c780b","tid":2227810,"uid":73856,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦你"},{"pid":"4554ebe6d756c6a1391be10320777227658071cb","tid":2227810,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:50:35.000Z","msg":"洗黑錢就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd805d5106d9e3581985e764acd5f37294f94db5","tid